oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mrs. Owen and her triplets
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Mrs. Martha Jane "Mattie" Moss Owen (1882-1947) and her newborn triplets. Woodrow Callis, Clayton Hoover, and McAdoo Clayton are lying on the bed with their mother. Two other women sit beside her bed.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Triplets; Births
